# clang-tidy overrides for Python bindings.
# nanobind uses macro-heavy metaprogramming (NB_MODULE, nb::class_, etc.) that
# confuses clang-tidy's static parser when run outside the full build graph.
# We disable clang-diagnostic-error here to prevent false positives from
# unresolved nanobind template expansions.
---
Checks: "-clang-diagnostic-error"
